definitions.definition: A town and civil parish with a town council in Somerset , England , previously in Somerset West and Taunton district ( OS grid ref ST2225 ) .
A suburb of Ashton-under-Lyne , Metropolitan Borough of Tameside , Greater Manchester , England ( OS grid ref SD9200 ) .
A place in the United States :

subdefinitions.definition: A city , the county seat of Bristol County , Massachusetts .
A minor city in Lyon County , Minnesota .
A hamlet in the town of Onondaga , Onondaga County , New York .
A town in Adams County , Washington .

definitions.definition: A rural locality in Gladstone Region, Queensland , Australia .
A locality in Barossa council area, South Australia .
